dct_title_s: Outline map of Southern Africa to illustrate the Analysis of Capt. Owen's voyage
dct_description_sm: Published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society by John Murray Albemarle Street, London 1833 ; W. Day, Gate St., Printer ; Lithographed by C. Bradbury.
Shows waterways, towns, various place names.
Taken from Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London, 1833, page 197/ 18550 (4).
